Package: prettyPanelMatch
Title: ggplot2-Based Visualization for PanelMatch (Imai et al. 2023) Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jihye", "Park", email = "Jihye.Park@unige.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2-based plotting functions for PanelMatch/PanelEstimate
    results. Converts PanelEstimate summary objects into tidy data frames and
    produces customizable coefficient plots with support for multiple models,
    moderator subgroups, and significance indicators.
